{"id": "gqo1665702761921", "title": "$SUPPRESS_UNCAUGHT_EXCEPTION_DIALOG", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "Configuration Reference", "Configuration Settings: Assignment", "[SETTINGS]", "$SUPPRESS_UNCAUGHT_EXCEPTION_DIALOG"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gqo1665702761921.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">$SUPPRESS_UNCAUGHT_EXCEPTION_DIALOG</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: $SUPPRESS_FORM_FEED \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: $SUPPRESS_FORM_FEED \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fbm1665702720519.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: $SYMBOL_TABLE \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: $SYMBOL_TABLE \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpw1665702656511.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/gqo1665702761921.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/gqo1665702761921.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/gqo1665702761921.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527972\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527972\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gqo1665702761921.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gqo1665702761921.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gqo1665702761921.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gqo1665702761921\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">If an uncaught exception occurs, suppress the dialog that displays the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerrorcontext</span> information about the cause of the exception.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"gqo1665702761921__topic_d143156e1_d143157e1_d143158e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gqo1665702761921__p_d143159e1_d143160e1_d143161e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SUPPRESS_UNCAUGHT_EXCEPTION_DIALOG</span> {= } <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">0</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gqo1665702761921__section_mpf_fyy_kwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d545860e68\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gqo1665702761921__table_d17255e1_d17256e1_d17257e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">application assignment file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gqo1665702761921__section_wwn_3yy_kwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d545860e114\">Description</h2>\n<div class=\"note important note_important\" id=\"gqo1665702761921__note_egn_ndj_gcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Important:</span> Use the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SUPPRESS_UNCAUGHT_EXCEPTION_DIALOG</span> setting only in situations\n            where a Windows or character mode application is run as part of an automated process\n            (such as automated testing). To suppress uncaught exceptions in a production\n            application, enclose the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">apstart </span>command within a\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">try-catch</code> block in the application apstart trigger.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gqo1665702761921__p_d143168e1_d143169e1_d143170e1\">By default, if an uncaught exception occurs, a form\n            is displayed containing the information provided by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerrorcontext</span>\n            about the error that caused the exception. This is intended behavior during application\n            development to ensure that the developer sees the exception and can fix the problem that\n            caused it.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gqo1665702761921__p_d143171e1_d143172e1_d143173e1\">However, this behavior can cause an automated test\n            to hang while it displays the form. To prevent the form from being displayed and ensure\n            that the exception information is not lost, complete these steps:</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\" id=\"gqo1665702761921__ol_wxg_jdj_gcc\">\n<li class=\"li\">Set <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SUPPRESS_UNCAUGHT_EXCEPTION_DIALOG</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=1</code>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">Specify a message log file using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$PUTMESS_LOGFILE</span> or a transcript\n               log file using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$TRANSCRIPT_LOGFILE</span>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p class=\"p\">The uncaught exception information is written to the log file specified by\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$PUTMESS_LOGFILE</span>. If this is not specified, it is written to the\n            console (on Windows, this is the <span class=\"keyword wintitle\">Transcript</span> window). If neither\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$PUTMESS_LOGFILE</span> nor <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$TRANSCRIPT_LOGFILE</span> are\n            specified, the information about the uncaught exception is written to the console on\n            Unix but lost on Windows.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zea1665702607771.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$PUTMESS_LOG_FILE</a><p>Copy the message frame contents to one or more files.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ttr1665702707353.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$TRANSCRIPT_LOG_FILE</a><p>Copy the Transcript window contents to file.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/opq1665702649630.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$procerrorcontext</a><p>Return the location of the error specified by $procerror.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ndy1677568050541.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Exception Handling</a><p>Exceptions are abnormal runtime events that may occur after executing a software instruction. Uncaught exceptions cause code execution to stop and the application to exit with a description of the error and where it occurred.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527972\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527972\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$SUPPRESS_UNCAUGHT_EXCEPTION_DIALOG Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 If an uncaught exception occurs, suppress the dialog that displays the $procerrorcontext information about the cause of the exception. $SUPPRESS_UNCAUGHT_EXCEPTION_DIALOG {= } 0 | 1 Defaults Assignment file: application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: None Description Important: Use the $SUPPRESS_UNCAUGHT_EXCEPTION_DIALOG setting only in situations where a Windows or character mode application is run as part of an automated process (such as automated testing). To suppress uncaught exceptions in a production application, enclose the apstart command within a try-catch block in the application apstart trigger. By default, if an uncaught exception occurs, a form is displayed containing the information provided by $procerrorcontext about the error that caused the exception. This is intended behavior during application development to ensure that the developer sees the exception and can fix the problem that caused it. However, this behavior can cause an automated test to hang while it displays the form. To prevent the form from being displayed and ensure that the exception information is not lost, complete these steps: Set $SUPPRESS_UNCAUGHT_EXCEPTION_DIALOG =1 . Specify a message log file using $PUTMESS_LOGFILE or a transcript log file using $TRANSCRIPT_LOGFILE . The uncaught exception information is written to the log file specified by $PUTMESS_LOGFILE . If this is not specified, it is written to the console (on Windows, this is the Transcript window). If neither $PUTMESS_LOGFILE nor $TRANSCRIPT_LOGFILE are specified, the information about the uncaught exception is written to the console on Unix but lost on Windows. Related Links $PUTMESS_LOG_FILE Copy the message frame contents to one or more files. $TRANSCRIPT_LOG_FILE Copy the Transcript window contents to file. $procerrorcontext Return the location of the error specified by $procerror. Exception Handling Exceptions are abnormal runtime events that may occur after executing a software instruction. Uncaught exceptions cause code execution to stop and the application to exit with a description of the error and where it occurred. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}